foyer bundles a single catch-all bezel — `default.png` — adapted from
libretro/common-overlays (https://github.com/libretro/common-overlays),
licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International:

  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

Source: borders/img/tv-integer.png  (generic CRT TV frame)

Per-system bezels live in the separate foyer-frontend/foyer-bezels
release catalogue and are installable on demand via foyer's
Settings → Updates → Install bezel packs.
